------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Hi Mudders from all over the world.

UNItopia is a german language MUD.

Here some basic commands translated for you:
   ende          quit
   schau         look
   sage	         say
   rede	         tell
   brülle        shout
   nimm          take
   lege	         drop
   gib		 give

For more sophisticated help try 'hilfe' or 'hilfe <command>'
